{"type":"text","timestamp":1771660605579,"sessionID":"ses_380ccb7b9ffed7jCNpL6Xw5pw4","part":{"id":"prt_c7f336dd3001pAEL0sFz5cH95u","sessionID":"ses_380ccb7b9ffed7jCNpL6Xw5pw4","messageID":"msg_c7f334895001jJiKyS27grfzKj","type":"text","text":"```dockerfile
# Build stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jdk-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /build

COPY pom.xml .
COPY src ./src

RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests && \
    mv target/*.jar app.jar

# Runtime stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

RUN apk add --no-cache fontconfig ttf-dejavu curl && \
    rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

WORKDIR /app

COPY aws-rds-ca-bundle.pem /tmp/aws-rds-ca-bundle.pem
COPY azure-digicert-ca.pem /tmp/azure-digicert-ca.pem

RUN keytool -importcert -alias aws-rds-ca -file /tmp/aws-rds-ca-bundle.pem -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    keytool -importcert -alias azure-digicert-ca -file /tmp/azure-digicert-ca.pem -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm -f /tmp/aws-rds-ca-bundle.pem /tmp/azure-digicert-ca.pem

COPY --from=builder /build/app.jar /app/app.jar

RUN addgroup -g 1001 app && \
    adduser -D -u 1001 -G app app && \
    chown -R app:app /app

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

LABEL maintainer="dev@example.com" \
      org.opencontainers.image.title="Analytics Dashboard"

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
